{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Marco Tempest: What I'd like to show you today"},{"time":2000,"text":"is something in the way of an experiment."},{"time":5000,"text":"Today's its debut."},{"time":7000,"text":"It's a demonstration of augmented reality."},{"time":10000,"text":"And the visuals you're about to see are not prerecorded."},{"time":13000,"text":"They are live"},{"time":15000,"text":"and reacting to me in real time."},{"time":17000,"text":"I like to think of it as a kind of technological magic."},{"time":22000,"text":"So fingers crossed."},{"time":25000,"text":"And keep your eyes on the big screen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29000,"text":"Augmented reality"},{"time":31000,"text":"is the melding of the real world"},{"time":34000,"text":"with computer-generated imagery."},{"time":37000,"text":"It seems the perfect medium"},{"time":39000,"text":"to investigate magic"},{"time":41000,"text":"and ask, why, in a technological age,"},{"time":44000,"text":"we continue to have"},{"time":46000,"text":"this magical sense of wonder."},{"time":49000,"text":"Magic is deception,"},{"time":52000,"text":"but it is a deception we enjoy."},{"time":55000,"text":"To enjoy being deceived,"},{"time":57000,"text":"an audience must first"},{"time":59000,"text":"suspend its disbelief."},{"time":61000,"text":"It was the poet Samuel Taylor Coleridge"},{"time":64000,"text":"who first suggested this receptive state of mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"Samuel Taylor Coleridge: I try to convey a semblance of truth in my writing"},{"time":71000,"text":"to produce for these shadows of the imagination"},{"time":74000,"text":"a willing suspension of disbelief"},{"time":77000,"text":"that, for a moment,"},{"time":79000,"text":"constitutes poetic faith."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"MT: This faith in the fictional is essential"},{"time":84000,"text":"for any kind of theatrical experience."},{"time":87000,"text":"Without it,"},{"time":89000,"text":"a script is just words."},{"time":91000,"text":"Augmented reality"},{"time":93000,"text":"is just the latest technology."},{"time":95000,"text":"And sleight of hand"},{"time":97000,"text":"is just an artful demonstration"},{"time":99000,"text":"of dexterity."},{"time":101000,"text":"We are all very good at suspending our disbelief."},{"time":103000,"text":"We do it every day,"},{"time":105000,"text":"while reading novels,"},{"time":107000,"text":"watching television"},{"time":109000,"text":"or going to the movies."},{"time":111000,"text":"We willingly enter fictional worlds"},{"time":113000,"text":"where we cheer our heroes"},{"time":115000,"text":"and cry for friends we never had."},{"time":118000,"text":"Without this ability"},{"time":120000,"text":"there is no magic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"It was Jean Robert-Houdin,"},{"time":124000,"text":"France's greatest illusionist,"},{"time":126000,"text":"who first recognized the role of the magician"},{"time":128000,"text":"as a storyteller."},{"time":130000,"text":"He said something that I've posted on the wall of my studio."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"Jean Robert-Houdin: A conjurer is not a juggler."},{"time":135000,"text":"He is an actor playing the part of a magician."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"MT: Which means magic is theater"},{"time":141000,"text":"and every trick"},{"time":143000,"text":"is a story."},{"time":145000,"text":"The tricks of magic"},{"time":147000,"text":"follow the archetypes of narrative fiction."},{"time":149000,"text":"There are tales of creation and loss,"},{"time":153000,"text":"death and resurrection,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and obstacles that must be overcome."},{"time":160000,"text":"Now many of them are intensely dramatic."},{"time":163000,"text":"Magicians play with fire and steel,"},{"time":165000,"text":"defy the fury of the buzzsaw,"},{"time":167000,"text":"dare to catch a bullet"},{"time":169000,"text":"or attempt a deadly escape."},{"time":173000,"text":"But audiences don't come to see the magician die,"},{"time":176000,"text":"they come to see him live."},{"time":178000,"text":"Because the best stories"},{"time":180000,"text":"always have a happy ending."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"The tricks of magic have one special element."},{"time":185000,"text":"They are stories with a twist."},{"time":188000,"text":"Now Edward de Bono argued"},{"time":190000,"text":"that our brains are pattern matching machines."},{"time":193000,"text":"He said that magicians deliberately exploit"},{"time":196000,"text":"the way their audiences think."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199000,"text":"Edward de Bono: Stage magic relies almost wholly"},{"time":201000,"text":"on the momentum error."},{"time":203000,"text":"The audience is led to make assumptions or elaborations"},{"time":206000,"text":"that are perfectly reasonable,"},{"time":208000,"text":"but do not, in fact, match"},{"time":210000,"text":"what is being done in front of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212000,"text":"MT: In that respect,"},{"time":214000,"text":"magic tricks are like jokes."},{"time":216000,"text":"Jokes lead us down a path"},{"time":219000,"text":"to an expected destination."},{"time":221000,"text":"But when the scenario we have imagined suddenly flips"},{"time":224000,"text":"into something entirely unexpected,"},{"time":226000,"text":"we laugh."},{"time":228000,"text":"The same thing happens"},{"time":230000,"text":"when people watch magic tricks."},{"time":232000,"text":"The finale"},{"time":235000,"text":"defies logic,"},{"time":237000,"text":"gives new insight into the problem,"},{"time":239000,"text":"and audiences express their amazement"},{"time":242000,"text":"with laughter."},{"time":244000,"text":"It's fun to be fooled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"One of the key qualities of all stories"},{"time":248000,"text":"is that they're made to be shared."},{"time":250000,"text":"We feel compelled to tell them."},{"time":252000,"text":"When I do a trick at a party --"},{"time":255000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":257000,"text":"that person will immediately pull their friend over"},{"time":259000,"text":"and ask me to do it again."},{"time":261000,"text":"They want to share the experience."},{"time":263000,"text":"That makes my job more difficult,"},{"time":265000,"text":"because, if I want to surprise them,"},{"time":267000,"text":"I need to tell a story that starts the same,"},{"time":269000,"text":"but ends differently --"},{"time":271000,"text":"a trick with a twist"},{"time":273000,"text":"on a twist."},{"time":275000,"text":"It keeps me busy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"Now experts believe"},{"time":279000,"text":"that stories go beyond our capacity for keeping us entertained."},{"time":283000,"text":"We think in narrative structures."},{"time":285000,"text":"We connect events and emotions"},{"time":289000,"text":"and instinctively transform them"},{"time":292000,"text":"into a sequence that can be easily understood."},{"time":295000,"text":"It's a uniquely human achievement."},{"time":297000,"text":"We all want to share our stories,"},{"time":299000,"text":"whether it is the trick we saw at the party,"},{"time":302000,"text":"the bad day at the office"},{"time":304000,"text":"or the beautiful sunset we saw on vacation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"Today, thanks to technology,"},{"time":310000,"text":"we can share those stories as never before,"},{"time":313000,"text":"by email, Facebook,"},{"time":316000,"text":"blogs, tweets,"},{"time":318000,"text":"on TED.com."},{"time":320000,"text":"The tools of social networking,"},{"time":323000,"text":"these are the digital campfires"},{"time":325000,"text":"around which the audience gathers"},{"time":327000,"text":"to hear our story."},{"time":329000,"text":"We turn facts into similes and metaphors,"},{"time":332000,"text":"and even fantasies."},{"time":334000,"text":"We polish the rough edges of our lives"},{"time":336000,"text":"so that they feel whole."},{"time":338000,"text":"Our stories make us the people we are"},{"time":341000,"text":"and, sometimes, the people we want to be."},{"time":344000,"text":"They give us our identity"},{"time":346000,"text":"and a sense of community."},{"time":349000,"text":"And if the story is a good one,"},{"time":352000,"text":"it might even make us smile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":364000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}